patthana10.10:1.1_0: Nasukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhāya vedanāya sampayutto
patthana10.10:1.1_1: nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nasukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ
patthana10.10:1.1_2: paṭicca nadukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Nasukhāya
patthana10.10:1.1_3: vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naadukkhamasukhāya vedanāya sampayutto
patthana10.10:2.1: Nadukkhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nadukkhāya vedanāya sampayutto nahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … satta. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana10.10:3.1: Naadukkhamasukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca … satta. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana10.10:5.1_0: Nasukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṁ nanahetuṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhāya vedanāya sampayutto
patthana10.10:5.1_1: nanahetu dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … pañca. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā catuvīsa …pe…
